subsection.p:
    Transformationas a machine
    It may help to think of T as a machine that takes x as an input, and gives you T(x) as the output.


\tikzset{
  pics/gear/.style args={#1/#2}{
    code = { % #1 = number of gears, #2 = tooth length
      \filldraw[fill=black!30] (1cm-#2/2,0)
